  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n1. as user A, add user B to contacts\r\n2. as user A, create community that requires approval to join\r\n3. as user A, add user B to that community\r\n4. as user B, observe the 1x1 chat with user A\r\n\r\n**As result:**\r\n\r\n- a community invitation bubble present, saying Go to the community\r\n- user is able to join the community by clicking it\r\n- Request to join button is shown at the top of channels list\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2022-11-16 at 10 51 42\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/202120857-1e2aeff2-9a52-4c0b-b60d-80b6a9ad9ec5.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2022-11-16 at 10 51 51\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/202120899-d2596726-4f9e-42fa-acaf-33ac7ce9e042.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected**:\r\n- community invitation should say \"Request to join\"\r\n- when clicked, the prompt to approve the memeber is sent to community owner\r\n- once approved, the joiner should see the \"go to community button\" in 1x1 chat\r\n\r\n**Version**: `0.8.0-rc.1`\r\n",
